 distribution of fruit bats throughout the Middle East, gene flow between colonies has not been altered by human activities. This discrepancy between habitat use and gene flow patterns may, therefore, be explained by the breeding system of the species and modifications of natal dispersal patterns.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Centeno\u2010Cuadros, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hulva, P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Romportl, D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Santoro, S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "St\u0159\u00edbn\u00e1, T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Shohami, D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Evin, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Tsoar, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Benda, P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hor\u00e1\u010dek, I.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Nathan, R.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/a6cc3d9634e4503bedb878e52619dbf6", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/e55c097a0552c9f9b95580d40b12c9edff2871531074c2d0602fc67606c65880", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/IK95Y224", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/IK95Y224", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/1f94220232f18bde445866870c4edf5e!/b44506-47003", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/26f7ce5dd404e33c6570edd4ba250d20", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal a